OL,3,CNew format for Newsnight from 28th May
OL,5,GThe date of the controversial changes
OL,6,Gto Newsnight has emerged. Schedules
OL,7,Greveal that the programme will be
OL,8,Gshortened on 28th May.
OL,10,FIt will run for 30 minutes with the
OL,11,Fweather following. The next programme
OL,12,Fwill start at 11.05pm.
OL,14,FThe revamped programme will focus
OL,15,Fprincipally on interviews and
OL,16,Fdiscussions. There will be less
OL,17,Fdedicated reporting.
OL,19,FThe changes are known to have been
OL,20,Fcontroversial within the BBC.
