OL,3,CNew format for Newsnight from 28th May
OL,5,FNewsnight had retained its own
OL,6,Fdedicated reporting team unlike other
OL,7,Fprogrammes.
OL,9,FFalling viewing figures, changes to
OL,10,Fthe way news is consumed and the state
OL,11,Fof BBC finances led to the cuts.
OL,13,FOne important question of course is
OL,14,Fwhether the new format will succeed or
OL,15,Fsimply seem like endless talk.
OL,17,FIt will be worth keeping an eye on the
OL,18,Fratings.
