OL,3,CNew format for Newsnight from 28th May
OL,5,FOne sad thing though is that such a
OL,6,Fsignificant change to a programme
OL,7,Fwhich once played a big part in
OL,8,Fmaintaining the BBC's corporate
OL,9,Freputation is almost going under the
OL,10,Fradar with politicians and the public.
OL,12,FNewsnight was once seen as important
OL,13,Fto the BBC's reputation with so-called
OL,14,Fopinion formers ` politicians, senior
OL,15,Fjournalists, those who had the ear of
OL,16,Fpeople in high places.
OL,18,FThat was one reason for the huge
OL,19,Finternal row in 1988 over whether it
OL,20,Fshould get a fixed starting time of
OL,21,F10.30pm.
