OL,3,CNew format for Newsnight from 28th May
OL,5,FOf course, the focus is increasingly
OL,6,Fon online and on-demand content.
OL,7,FJournalists are expected to work
OL,8,Facross all platforms as appropriate.
OL,10,FWill the kind of original journalism
OL,11,Fand analysis which Newsnight has
OL,12,Fproduced with distinction survive on
OL,13,Fother platforms?
OL,15,FThis needs proper monitoring.
OL,17,FThe name has survived and a late-night
OL,18,Finterview and discussion programme may
OL,19,Fwell find an audience.
OL,21,FBut the kind of journalism the
OL,22,Fprogramme championed must survive too.
